  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2577860/extras/4395a297a84dc1bf152699ab26bdd364.avif?t=1711102459\" width=652 height=220 /></span><br><br>It was raining und thunderstorming.<br>In the middle of the night.<br>And there happened something ...<br>... something terrible.<br><br>At the old abandoned ... WATERMILL.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2577860/extras/3eb5028566c44e867aa8f84aecd01924.poster.avif?t=1711102459\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2577860/extras/3eb5028566c44e867aa8f84aecd01924.webm?t=1711102459\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2577860/extras/3eb5028566c44e867aa8f84aecd01924.mp4?t=1711102459\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2577860/extras/6fd72375570d2e19fef319092994e4f7.webp?t=1711102459\" width=620 height=31 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>Point and click</strong> adventure <br></li><li> Simple and clean interface<br></li><li> Vast narrative - Experience the story parts by <strong>exploring</strong><br></li><li> Handdrawn <strong>comic-art</strong><br></li><li> Thrilling ambience sound and suspenseful <strong>soundtrack</strong><br></li><li> Short playtime (~45min-1 hour)<br></li><li> 3 different game endings</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2577860/extras/738bc77482ab23de44a3b0f8c3c56e2f.poster.avif?t=1711102459\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.